        "color_scheme": "scheme-4",
        "subtext": "",
        "text": "<p>Our journey didn't begin in a design studio, but in the rigorous worlds of <strong>science, mathematics, and engineering</strong>. We looked to the Greek symbol λ (lambda)—a character that defines the very structure of the physical world. By choosing a symbol rooted in precision and efficiency, we ensured that HNDRD was born with a \"performance-first\" DNA. </p>",
