      "name": "t:sections.studio-text.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "color_scheme": "scheme-4",
        "subtext": "",
        "text": "<p>While the static Lambda was <strong>elegant</strong>, it did not carry the uncompromising weight we demanded.<br/><br/>We began to <strong>strip away the excess</strong> and <strong>sharpen the geometry</strong>. We slashed the feet perfectly horizontal to the ground plane, planting it firmly. The decorative curves were shaved off.<br/><br/>This step represents our absolute commitment to <strong>eradicate the performative and non-essentials</strong>. The curves, while historically aesthetically pleasing, served no real purpose. </p>",
